	dprr:hasNoteText "Named in the Bembinus Ms of the Didascalia of Terence Eun. (see note 1). Dziatzko's dating in 146 (RhM 21 [1866] 66) is doubted by Seidel (FA 79) since it is unlikely that in this period a plebeian and a patrician would be colleagues in this office." .
